children.subject: Andrea Mejia Valencia is available for advising appointments (as soon as this afternoon) for EECS Majors: https://andreamejia.youcanbook.me/index.jsp

history.content:
Welcome back!

We are excited for your return from the summer break! Here are a few updates to get your semester started.

|

L&S CS Advising appointments can now be made through the "Appointments" Portal in CalCentral. Find out more about how to sign up.
  • The L&S CS Advising team will also offer drop-in appointments for quick questions 10am to 4pm Wednesday in 315, 377, 379 Soda
  • *We are closed for lunch 12pm-1pm*  
  • The 2017-2018 L&S Computer Science FAQ document can be found here. If you have suggestions, please let us know. 
EECS Students may continue scheduling appointments through berkeleyeecs.youcanbook.me
  • You're welcome to come by 205 Cory for quick questions, although we might not always be available. Our hours are 9am-12pm and 1-4pm 
  • We're also in the process of hiring a new Adviser...stay tuned

Enrollment Questions (please check Piazza for your question first)

  • Computer Science courses: Cindy is located in 379 Soda Hall. Her drop-in hours are Monday through Friday 10am-12pm & 1-3pm.
  • Electrical Engineering and EECS courses: Lydia is located in 205 Cory Hall. Her drop-in hours are Monday & Wednesday 11am-12pm & 2-4pm and Fridays 11am-12pm.

Staying Connected: 
Student Organizations
Facebook Page
We look forward to seeing you soon!
